uite the sort of trustless decentralized blah blah blah that crypto promise=
s.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So what=E2=80=99s to stop those two huma=
ns from running off with the money, or the Constitution?[5] The answer=C2=
=A0<em>absolutely cannot be=C2=A0</em>=E2=80=9Cthe immutable code of a smar=
t contract on the blockchain,=E2=80=9D because the Constitution is a piece =
